Rinse and trim chicken breast. Grill on each side 5 to 7 minutes and remove from heat. Let stand for 5 minutes then slice into strips. Salt and pepper to taste. Rinse and dry mixed lettuces and place in a large bowl along with green onion. Lightly dress with Raspberry & Walnut Salad Dressing, and arrange lettuces on dinner plates. Arrange orange and grapefruit sections, avocado and onion slices, and chicken on top of lettuce. Drizzle additional Raspberry & Walnut Salad Dressing to taste. Garnish with fresh raspberries.